# WordPress Reference

## Identity
Domain: `'skel'` | Prefix: `skel_`

## Template Hierarchy
```
Front: front-page.php → home.php → index.php
Single: single-{type}.php → single.php → index.php
Page: page-{slug}.php → page.php → index.php
Archive: archive-{type}.php → archive.php → index.php
```

## Hooks
```php
add_action( 'after_setup_theme', 'skel_setup' );
add_action( 'wp_enqueue_scripts', 'skel_enqueue_scripts' );
add_filter( 'body_class', 'skel_body_classes' );
```
